CONCEPT 1: MDC AND SDC

MDC (Mega-Damage Capacity) applies to power armor, robots, and mega-damage
creatures. Only MDC-rated weapons and certain powers harm MDC targets reliably.

SDC (Structural Damage Capacity) plus Hit Points applies to most humans,
animals, and ordinary objects.

See help combat and help weapons for current in-game behavior.

